summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Pine Street from Westlake Avenue to the alley between Seventh and Eighth Avenue et al in the City of Seattle, by planking under Ordinance No. 18406, creating Local Improvement District No. 1735 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
